name: The All Hopeful Limbuk 001
description:
Limbuk is a maid from Indonesia's Wayang universe. With her mom, Cangik, they become one of the comical characters in the mostly "serious" wayang fragment. Limbuk is a very confidence person who's in love with Arjuna, one of the main character on the Mahabharata epic, of course, it's a platonic love.

Part of a collaborative series with my own mother, this painting is originaly made with coffee liquid on canvas
